Storage?

00:27:53.130 --> 00:27:57.230
FELICIA: Oh, well. It's a really long story. Can I
tell you all about it?

00:27:57.230 --> 00:27:58.928
SAM: Abridged. Abridged.

00:27:58.928 --> 00:28:00.753
LAURA: Grog look, papaya.

00:28:00.953 --> 00:28:01.967
TRAVIS: Rah!

00:28:01.967 --> 00:28:03.704
FELICIA: I guess some of it's still clean.

