01:51:15.167 --> 01:51:16.481
SAM: Fuck you!

01:51:16.481 --> 01:51:18.276
(laughter)

01:51:18.276 --> 01:51:23.442
MATT: And that's-- Oh, and the two on Percy, who
are now looking for retribution. They're looking

01:51:23.442 --> 01:51:26.036
