01:51:31.243 --> 01:51:33.468
FELICIA: Manic pixie dream gunslinger.

01:51:33.468 --> 01:51:34.521
TALIESIN: Thank you.

01:51:34.521 --> 01:51:35.997
MATT: That'll be a 20.

01:51:35.997 --> 01:51:36.948
TALIESIN: I walked into that.

01:51:36.948 --> 01:51:37.878
MATT: 20 to hit.

01:51:37.878 --> 01:51:41.528
TALIESIN: I'm going to spend a Grit point and--
