01:52:13.117 --> 01:52:14.276
LAURA: Oh no!

01:52:14.276 --> 01:52:17.962
MATT: You take four points of damage from one.
Rolled really low.

01:52:17.962 --> 01:52:20.554
That one rolled pretty high, you take 12.

01:52:20.612 --> 01:52:21.663
TALIESIN: 12 total?

