01:57:31.504 --> 01:57:33.548
LAURA: Yes! Have a meal, buddy!

01:57:33.548 --> 01:57:35.815
TRAVIS: Oh yeah, you want to cuddle with that?

01:57:35.815 --> 01:57:37.281
LAURA: Hell yeah I do!

