MATT: Zahra, it's your go.

01:57:39.037 --> 01:57:42.327
MARY: All right. Is that an orc right behind me?

01:57:42.327 --> 01:57:44.693
MATT: This is Vex right there.

01:57:44.693 --> 01:57:46.094
LAURA: That's me.

01:57:46.094 --> 01:57:47.645
MARY: No, I can't see where I am.

01:57:47.645 --> 01:57:49.208
MATT: You're right here.

01:57:49.208 --> 01:57:52.199
