01:59:16.146 --> 01:59:18.764
MARY: 13 plus 11.

01:59:18.764 --> 01:59:20.488
LAURA: So 24.

01:59:20.488 --> 01:59:21.548
MARY: 24.

01:59:21.548 --> 01:59:22.856
MATT: That hits.

